{"tid":2249188,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者：港激發全球抗專政","createTime":"2020-10-19T07:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T08:34:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd7b28c13d98c03a0b80acf60dd7ddbea0928c98","tid":2249188,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/T64PSZZFB5GHJKTKSVWUSZVNTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FT64PSZZFB5GHJKTKSVWUSZVNTI%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Znobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=a64c4f38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FT64PSZZFB5GHJKTKSVWUSZVNTI%2F&h=c8ec2379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/T64PSZZFB5GHJKTKSVWUSZVNTI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n學者：港激發全球抗專政<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kXBQoCYBA6mIBfoH55-NP5kmZ5M=/1769x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KE2XWDQUGNFO5FQ4PUG5D64U4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkXBQoCYBA6mIBfoH55-NP5kmZ5M%3D%2F1769x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKE2XWDQUGNFO5FQ4PUG5D64U4E.jpg&h=726147ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■在曼谷勝利紀念碑聚集的大批示威者為救護車讓出車道。 路透社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】泰國示威浪潮不少地方有香港抗爭運動的影子。美國有歷史學者認為，香港抗爭運動已改變世界，去年反送中運動強調的「如水」（be water）精神，前所未有令全球多處對抗專政的力量遍地開花。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：抗爭者促德禁泰王旅居  君主制爭拗 泰爆兩代撕裂<br />\n<br />\n美國加州大學歐文分校歷史學教授華志堅（Jeffrey Wasserstrom）昨在《日本經濟新聞》撰文指，香港抗爭者2014年和去年發起大規模運動，都未能推進民主進程，但從白羅斯明斯克、美國明尼蘇達州、黎巴嫩貝魯特及泰國曼谷的示威者表達訴求的方式可見，香港抗爭顯然鼓舞和影響全球各地對抗專制政權的獨特抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n滅催淚彈等戰略遍地開花<br />\n<br />\n他指1989年六四事件抗爭者遭血腥鎮壓，未成功爭取他們渴望的自由，但仍影響幾代人，包括香港抗爭者。2014年雨傘運動國際矚目，即使未成功爭取普選，但去年再吸引群眾走上街頭，由反送中演變成對抗政權打壓和警暴的抗爭，持續更長時間及更引令全球注目。《逃犯條例》修訂終被撤回。<br />\n<br />\n雖然北京實施港版國安法令異見人士更易被送中，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"e9f07f8be9347af771965bf7278e0376996b72c9","tid":2249188,"uid":116547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:33:30.000Z","msg":"由各區開花到各國開花"},{"pid":"a0aac0906eacc907d689e45b8df5b6b0beae6582","tid":2249188,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"踩港撚：食黄店抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b060a2015d242ead196652e202e58821b7e6a5db","tid":2249188,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"香港人，勁  ！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}